<!-- -->5. <span class="anon-block">K. I.</span>
</strong>, <span class="anon-block">ur. (...)</span> w <span class="anon-block">S.</span>, syna <span class="anon-block">Z.</span> i <span class="anon-block">D.</span> z d. <span class="anon-block">D.</span>
